## Passage Data — CC BY-NC 4.0

Applies to: `data/passages.jsonl`, `data/passage_edges.jsonl`, `texts/`

The passage corpus is derived from source translations with varying licenses:

- **Public domain translations** (Anattalakkhana Sutta / Sujato, Milindapanha
  / Rhys Davids, Diamond Sutra, Sunyatasaptati / Lindtner, Vimalakirti /
  Thurman, Bodhicharyavatara / Padmakara, MMK / Geshe Kelsang Wangmo,
  Heart Sutra): no restrictions on use.

- **84000 translations** (Ashtasahasrika Prajnaparamita, Samdhinirmocana
  Sutra): licensed CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 by 84000: Translating the Words of the
  Buddha. These passages may not be used for commercial purposes or in
  modified form without permission from 84000.
  See: https://84000.co/terms-of-use

Because the corpus as a whole includes 84000 material, the combined
`passages.jsonl` and `passage_edges.jsonl` files are made available under
**CC BY-NC 4.0** (non-commercial use, attribution required). If you use only
passages from non-84000 sources, those passages carry no additional
restrictions beyond their original public domain status.

Full license text: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/

